A vast network of glowing fiber optic cables arranged in a wheel-and-spoke pattern, viewed from above in a dark cyberpunk cityscape at night. The central hub pulses with intense cyan and magenta light, with multiple luminous pathways radiating outward to smaller glowing nodes at the edges. Data streams visualized as tiny particles of light flow bidirectionally along the cables, some taking direct shortcuts between outer nodes while others route through the brilliant center. Rain-slicked surfaces below reflect the ethereal network glow. The architecture feels alive, organic yet technological, with steam rising from vents and holographic grid overlays floating above the connections. Deep purple shadows contrast with neon highlights, creating dramatic depth and movement throughout the interconnected system.
